text: <@U26BLKGE4> the old site was WP so we just left everything there so we didn't have to migrate anything lol... the lazy option but it'd probably be just as easy setting it up with HubSpot CMS

we are using HubSpot tracking script as the only analytics on the site to keep things speedy, HubSpot submit form API for the form in the footer (also to keep things speedy vs a form embed), and the meetings embed on the contact page.
